    {
      "id": "content-editor-periodic",
      "name": "content-editor-periodic",
      "prompt": "## Slot Gap Fill + QA\n\nThe 3h30m publish slots are: 05:30 → 09:00 → 12:30 → 16:00 → 19:30 → 23:00 → 02:30(+1d) → 06:00(+1d). Running now — figure out which slot this run corresponds to (the slot just ending).\n\n### Step 1: Check previous slot\nQuery recent posts: `wp post list --post_status=publish,future --posts_per_page=15 --orderby=date --order=desc`.\nIf NO post matches the previous slot (check post_date KST), fill the gap:\n  - Read `~/.drewgent/P4-cortex/content/content-backlog.md` — pick highest-priority ready item\n  - If backlog empty, check ~/.drewgent/kanban.db for pending content tasks\n  - Write 500-800 words, 반말, 1인칭, Gutenberg HTML\n  - Publish to the missed slot: `docker exec humanerd-wp wp --allow-root post create --post_title=\"...\" --post_content=\"...\" --post_status=publish --post_author=1 --post_name=kebab-slug --category=<slug> --date=\"YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM:00\"`\n  - Set meta: `wp post meta update <ID> _yoast_wpseo_metadesc \"...\"`\n  - Also update ~/.drewgent/P4-cortex/content/narrative-arc.md with new post\n\n### Step 2: QA drafts\n1. `wp post list --post_status=draft --posts_per_page=10`\n2. Fix author, Gutenberg HTML, voice, AI-isms\n3. If acceptable → `wp post update <ID> --post_status=publish`\n\n### Step 3: QA recent publishes\n1. `wp post list --post_status=publish --posts_per_page=10` — check last 6h\n2. Fix post_author, meta description, category\n3. Report summary",
